description:
Here they are more obscure Infrogames games. All 6 Space Quest games. Just mount the .iso onto a virtual drive open it and copy both folders and all their contents to your HDD and then run both setup,exe and play.

Yes you will need a DOS emulator for this as well I use DOSbox you can download the latest version here:
 &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.dosbox.com/download.php?main=1&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.dosbox.com/download.php?main=1&lt;/a&gt;

These games come from www.GOG.com they are DRM free so share them with your friends no hacks, cracks, or patches needed.

I STRONGLY recommend that you download and install DOSbox first if yo haven't already then run the install files.
